transcript:
[Ringing]
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello. Ya, hi sir. Wo wo hamara hamara manager abhi tak nahi aaya tha. Main tumhe call back karta hu wo aate hi. Sir, maine mera WhatsApp pe message dala hai aap wo mujhe pe call kar lijiyega isko nahi lagega call to, theek na?
Customer: Mil gaya mil gaya dekha okay.
Executive: Okay sir okay okay thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Manager not available.

- Request to call back on WhatsApp.



Resolution:

- Executive will call back when the manager arrives.

- Customer acknowledged receiving the WhatsApp message.



Next Steps: 

Issue not resolved. Executive will call back when the manager arrives.

Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

Neutral to positive.

manager availability, whatsapp call
